# =============================================
# API 测试用例
# 适用于 VS Code REST Client 插件
# 使用方法：点击每个请求上方的 "Send Request"
# =============================================

# -------------------- 全局变量 --------------------
# 请手动替换 <token> 为实际登录后获取的 JWT 令牌
# 替换 <uid> 为具体用户 uid

### --------------------------------------------------
### 健康检查
### --------------------------------------------------
GET http://localhost:3001/api/health


### ==================================================
### 认证模块
### ==================================================

### 用户注册（需管理员权限，测试环境可由管理员手动执行）
POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "newuser",
  "password": "SecurePass123!",
  "department": "soft",
  "role": "internal"
}

### 用户登录（成功后会返回 token，请复制到上方变量）
POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "administrator",
  "password": "qdezJDS"
}


### ==================================================
### 用户模块（需要认证，在 Header 中替换 token）
### ==================================================

### 查看自己的完整信息
GET http://localhost:3001/api/user/me/profile
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### 查看他人的公开信息（替换 <uid>）
GET http://localhost:3001/api/user/<uid>
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### 修改用户名（3天冷却）
PATCH http://localhost:3001/api/user/me/username
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <token>

{
  "newUsername": "newname123"
}

### 修改密码
PATCH http://localhost:3001/api/user/me/password
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <token>

{
  "oldPassword": "SecurePass123!",
  "newPassword": "NewSecurePass456!"
}

### 修改个人资料（简介、真实姓名、主题色、联系方式）
PATCH http://localhost:3001/api/user/me/profile
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <token>

{
  "real_name": "张三",
  "bio": "热爱机械设计",
  "theme_color": "#ff6600",
  "contacts": [
    { "platform": "QQ", "handle": "123456" },
    { "platform": "微信", "handle": "wxid_test" }
  ]
}

### 上传头像（需要 multipart/form-data）
POST http://localhost:3001/api/user/me/avatar
Authorization: Bearer <token>
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="avatar"; filename="avatar.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< /path/to/your/avatar.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary--

### 上传背景图
POST http://localhost:3001/api/user/me/cover
Authorization: Bearer <token>
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="cover"; filename="cover.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< /path/to/your/cover.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary--

### 获取某用户最近帖子（替换 <uid>）
GET http://localhost:3001/api/user/<uid>/posts?limit=4
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### 获取当前用户的封禁状态
GET http://localhost:3001/api/user/me/bans
Authorization: Bearer <token>


### ==================================================
### 论坛模块
### ==================================================

### 获取所有板块列表
GET http://localhost:3001/api/forum/categories
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### 获取某个板块的帖子列表（分页，替换 slug）
GET http://localhost:3001/api/forum/announcements/posts?page=1&pageSize=10&sortBy=time
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### 按热度排序帖子
GET http://localhost:3001/api/forum/general/posts?sortBy=hot
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### 获取帖子详情（替换 slug 和 postId）
GET http://localhost:3001/api/forum/announcements/posts/1
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### 发布新帖（在指定板块下，替换 slug）
POST http://localhost:3001/api/forum/announcements/posts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <token>

{
  "title": "测试帖子标题",
  "content": "这是一篇 **Markdown** 格式的测试帖子，支持数学公式 $E=mc^2$。"
}

### 修改帖子权限（管理员/版主，替换 slug 和 postId）
PATCH http://localhost:3001/api/forum/announcements/posts/1/permission
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <token>

{
  "field": "can_reply",
  "value": false
}

### 删除帖子（作者/管理员/版主）
DELETE http://localhost:3001/api/forum/announcements/posts/1
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### ---------- 评论与回复 ----------

### 获取帖子的评论列表（分页，替换 slug 和 postId）
GET http://localhost:3001/api/forum/announcements/posts/1/comments?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### 发表评论
POST http://localhost:3001/api/forum/announcements/posts/1/comments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <token>

{
  "content": "这篇帖子写得很好！"
}

### 获取某个评论的回复列表（分页，替换 commentId）
GET http://localhost:3001/api/forum/comments/1/replies?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### 发表回复（直接回复评论）
POST http://localhost:3001/api/forum/comments/1/replies
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <token>

{
  "content": "同意你的观点",
  "replyToUserId": 2,
  "parentReplyId": null
}

### 发表对回复的回复（二级回复，parentReplyId 为被回复的回复ID）
POST http://localhost:3001/api/forum/comments/1/replies
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <token>

{
  "content": "回复 @testuser1：你说得对",
  "replyToUserId": 3,
  "parentReplyId": 1
}

### 删除评论（作者/管理员/版主，替换 slug 和 commentId）
DELETE http://localhost:3001/api/forum/comments/1
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### 删除回复（作者/管理员/版主，替换 slug 和 replyId）
DELETE http://localhost:3001/api/forum/replies/1
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### 获取板块禁言状态
GET http://localhost:3001/api/forum/category/1/ban-status
Authorization: Bearer <token>


### ==================================================
### 网盘模块
### ==================================================

### 获取私有网盘文件列表
GET http://localhost:3001/api/cloud/private
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### 上传私有文件
POST http://localhost:3001/api/cloud/private
Authorization: Bearer <token>
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="document.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< /path/to/your/file.pdf
------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="type"

private
------WebKitFormBoundary--

### 下载私有文件（替换 fileId）
GET http://localhost:3001/api/cloud/private/1/download
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### 删除私有文件（替换 fileId）
DELETE http://localhost:3001/api/cloud/private/1
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### 获取公共网盘文件列表（按部门，替换 department：art/mech/soft）
GET http://localhost:3001/api/cloud/public/art
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### 上传公共文件（替换 department）
POST http://localhost:3001/api/cloud/public
Authorization: Bearer <token>
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="design.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< /path/to/your/design.png
------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="type"

public
------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="department"

art
------WebKitFormBoundary--

### 下载公共文件（替换 fileId）
GET http://localhost:3001/api/cloud/public/1/download
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### 删除公共文件（替换 fileId）
DELETE http://localhost:3001/api/cloud/public/1
Authorization: Bearer <token>


### ==================================================
### 管理员模块（需管理员 token）
### ==================================================

### 获取用户列表（搜索、分页）
GET http://localhost:3001/api/admin/users?page=1&pageSize=20&q=test
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### 获取板块列表
GET http://localhost:3001/api/admin/categories
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### 封禁用户（禁止发帖1小时）
POST http://localhost:3001/api/admin/ban
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <token>

{
  "userId": 2,
  "type": "post",
  "duration": "1h"
}

### 永久禁止用户使用网盘
POST http://localhost:3001/api/admin/ban
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <token>

{
  "userId": 2,
  "type": "cloud",
  "duration": null
}

### 解封用户（解禁发帖）
POST http://localhost:3001/api/admin/unban
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <token>

{
  "userId": 2,
  "type": "post"
}

### 授予版主（userId 和 categoryId 替换为实际值）
POST http://localhost:3001/api/admin/grant-mod
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <token>

{
  "userId": 2,
  "categoryId": 1
}

### 撤销版主
POST http://localhost:3001/api/admin/revoke-mod
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <token>

{
  "userId": 2,
  "categoryId": 1
}

### 获取单个用户的封禁详情
GET http://localhost:3001/api/admin/user/2/bans
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### 设置板块禁言（categoryId 为板块ID）
POST http://localhost:3001/api/admin/category/1/ban
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### 解除板块禁言
DELETE http://localhost:3001/api/admin/category/1/ban
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### 获取板块禁言状态
GET http://localhost:3001/api/admin/category/1/ban-status
Authorization: Bearer <token>